SUB_W07_EVAR_SIUG_MISSION_141_CUT_000_02.text:
Ah, you must be the Soul Voyager.
The temple told us you'd be coming;
we are excited to behold your success.

SUB_W07_EVAR_SIUG_MISSION_301_CUT_000_02.text:
I would suggest you deploy a fiend;
it should take no more than a minor
fright to send this rabble packing.

SUB_W07_FUNC_SIUG_MISSIONCONFIRMATION_TE.text:
